tellraw @s ["",{text:"This Datapack provides:",bold:true},{text:"\ndialog GUI to create Teams\n- Display Name and Color (will be displayed in front of the player's name)\n- a name field for the game-code (just enter the Name without spaces and special Caracters)\n- after creating you get a 6-digit Code for joining\n- available with the command "},{text:"/dialog show @s teams:add",italic:true,click_event:{action:"suggest_command",command:"/dialog show @s teams:add"}},{text:" for operators level 2 and aboth\n\n/trigger command to join\n- use "},{text:"/trigger Team set <code>",italic:true,click_event:{action:"suggest_command",command:"/trigger Team set <code>"}},{text:" to enter the Code\n- negative values let you leave the Team\n- just "},{text:"/trigger Team",italic:true,click_event:{action:"suggest_command",command:"/trigger Team"}},{text:" to get the Code of the current Team\n- 10 minutes Cooldown for joining (can be adjusted via "},{text:"/scoreboard players set .Cooldown Team_Cooldown <time in ticks>",italic:true,click_event:{action:"suggest_command",command:"/scoreboard players set .Cooldown Team_Cooldown <time in ticks>"}},{text:" 12000 by default)\n- available for everyone (operator level 0 and aboth)\n\nlist-function\n- lists all Teams in pages of 10 per page\n- buttons for joining, removing the Team and listing it's Members\n- clicking on the page-counter, suggests a command for changing the page ("},{text:"<number>",italic:true},{text:" has to be replaced)\n- avaialabe with "},{text:"/function teams:list",italic:true,click_event:{action:"suggest_command",command:"/function teams:list"}},{text:" to operators (level 2+)\n\nfunction to load generated Teams on new world\n1. copy "},{text:"command_storage_teams.dat",italic:true},{text:" from the data folder in your old world folder and paste it at the same place in your new world folder\n2. load Datapack and run "},{text:"/function teams:take_copy",italic:true,click_event:{action:"suggest_command",command:"/function teams:take_copy1"}},{text:"\n3. Teams are being copied to new world with same Team-Codes\n4. Players can get Team-Codes of old world with "},{text:"/trigger Team",italic:true,click_event:{action:"suggest_command",command:"/trigger Team"}},{text:" and rejoin the old Team with them\n\nunistall function\n- "},{text:"/function teams:uninstall",italic:true,click_event:{action:"suggest_command",command:"/function teams:uninstall"}},{text:"\n- disables the datapack\n- removes Teams (can be reloaded with "},{text:"/function teams:take_copy1",italic:true,click_event:{action:"suggest_command",command:"/function teams:take_copy1"}},{text:" like described aboth starting at 2.)\n\nhelp function\n- shows this text\n- "},{text:"/function teams:help",italic:true,click_event:{action:"suggest_command",command:"/function teams:help"}}]